    <title>
        <en>Realistic Animal Names</en>
        <de>Realistische Tiernamen</de>
        <fr>Noms d'Animaux Réalistes</fr>
        <pl>Realistyczne Nazwy Zwierząt</pl>
        <es>Nombres Realistas para Animales</es>
        <it>Nomi Animali Realistici</it>
        <cz>Realistická Jména Zvířat</cz>
        <br>Nomes Realistas de Animais</br>
        <uk>Реалістичні Імена Тварин</uk>
        <ru>Реалистичные Имена Животных</ru>
        <hu>Realista Állatnevek</hu>
        <nl>Realistische Dierennamen</nl>
        <ro>Nume Realiste pentru Animale</ro>
    </title>

    <description>
        <en><![CDATA[Add custom names to your animals with floating name tags displayed above them.

Features:
• Custom name input for each animal
• Floating name tags with distance-based scaling
• Configurable display settings
• Toggle visibility in settings menu
• Per-savegame name storage
• Keybind support (default: K)
• Full multiplayer synchronization (v2.2.0+)
• API for other mods to read/write names

Usage:
1. Walk near an animal (within configurable distance)
2. Press K to open naming dialog
3. Enter custom name (supports UTF-8 characters)
4. Adjust settings in game settings menu

All names are saved per savegame and sync across all players in multiplayer.]]></en>
        <de><![CDATA[Fügen Sie Ihren Tieren benutzerdefinierte Namen mit schwebenden Namensschildern hinzu. Perfekte Multiplayer-Synchronisierung.]]></de>
        <fr><![CDATA[Ajoutez des noms personnalisés à vos animaux avec des étiquettes flottantes. Synchronisation multijoueur parfaite.]]></fr>
        <es><![CDATA[Añade nombres personalizados a tus animales con etiquetas flotantes. Sincronización multijugador perfecta.]]></es>
    </description>

    <iconFilename>icon.dds</iconFilename>
    <multiplayer supported="true"/>

    <!-- Settings integrated with game settings menu -->
    <settings>
        <setting name="ran_showNames" 
                 title="ran_setting_showNames" 
                 type="bool" 
                 default="true" />
        
        <setting name="ran_nameDistance" 
                 title="ran_setting_nameDistance" 
                 type="float" 
                 default="15" 
                 min="5" 
                 max="50" />
        
        <setting name="ran_nameHeight" 
                 title="ran_setting_nameHeight" 
                 type="float" 
                 default="1.8" 
                 min="0.5" 
                 max="3.0" />
        
        <setting name="ran_fontSize" 
                 title="ran_setting_fontSize" 
                 type="float" 
                 default="0.018" 
                 min="0.010" 
                 max="0.030" />
    </settings>

    <!-- Input Actions -->
    <actions>
        <action name="RAN_OPEN_UI" 
                category="VEHICLE" 
                axisType="HALF" />
    </actions>

    <!-- Default Keybindings -->
    <inputBinding>
        <actionBinding action="RAN_OPEN_UI">
            <binding device="KB_MOUSE_DEFAULT" input="KEY_k" />
        </actionBinding>
    </inputBinding>

